Darkfate/Blacknightmare::

Darkfate "Follow me Orchestra, we can speak about in the Command-
room" said the male "Blacknighmare, go with Drillbit and told him 
that we need speak after that come to Command-room"

Blacknightmare nodded. 

Darkfate told to Orchestra "Follow me"  

The male started to walk, Blacknightmare looked to Orchestra, she 
smiled and kindly she said "Follow him"
